    <item>
      <title>Proofread and double-check your paper before submission</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/en/proofread-and-double-check-your-paper-before-submission/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 May 2007 20:38:31 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/en/proofread-and-double-check-your-paper-before-submission/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/zh/proofread-and-double-check-your-paper-before-submission.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/proofread-and-double-check-your-paper-before-submission/&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/proofread-and-double-check-your-paper-before-submission/&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/proofread-and-double-check-your-paper-before-submission/&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;proofread-and-double-check-your-paper-before-submission&#34;&gt;Proofread and double-check your paper before submission&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;过而不改，是谓过矣 [A man who has committed a mistake and doesn&amp;rsquo;t correct it, is committing another mistake.]&lt;br&gt;&#xA;(孔夫子 &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Confucius&#34;&gt;Confucius&lt;/a&gt;, &amp;ldquo;論語 &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Analects&#34;&gt;Analects&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rdquo;)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Nobody, least of all referees, enjoys a paper which is badly written and full of errors.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Even if the result itself is first-class, a cavalier attitude to expository or accuracy issues (or the presumption that it is solely up to the editor and referee, rather than the author, to address these issues) will negatively impact both the referee reports on the paper, and the editor&amp;rsquo;s final decision on the paper. (Even if the paper does eventually appear, these issues may also discourage potential readers from working their way through the paper.)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Submit a final draft, not a first draft</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/en/submit-a-final-draft-not-a-first-draft/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 May 2007 20:13:18 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/en/submit-a-final-draft-not-a-first-draft/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/zh/submit-a-final-draft-not-a-first-draft.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/submit-a-final-draft-not-a-first-draft/&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/submit-a-final-draft-not-a-first-draft/&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/submit-a-final-draft-not-a-first-draft/&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;submit-a-final-draft-not-a-first-draft&#34;&gt;Submit a final draft, not a first draft&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s not at all important to get it right the first time. It&amp;rsquo;s vitally important to get it right the last time.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;— Andrew Hunt and David Thomas, &amp;ldquo;The pragmatic programmer&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is a corollary to &amp;ldquo;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/en/proofread-and-double-check-your-paper-before-submission/&#34;&gt;Proofread and double-check your paper before submission&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Use the wastebasket</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/career-advice/orig/use-the-wastebasket/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 May 2007 19:05:14 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/career-advice/orig/use-the-wastebasket/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/career-advice/zh/use-the-wastebasket.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/use-the-wastebasket/&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/use-the-wastebasket/&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/use-the-wastebasket/&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;use-the-wastebasket&#34;&gt;Use the wastebasket&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It is a mistake to suppose that men succeed through success; they much oftener succeed through failures. Precept, study, advice, and example could never have taught them so well as failure has done.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Samuel Smiles&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Not every idea leads to a success, and not every first draft forms a good template for the final draft.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
